<h2 id="四二叉树问题">四、二叉树问题</h2>

<h3 id="1实现二叉树的先序中序后序遍历包括递归方式和非递归">1、实现二叉树的先序、中序、后序遍历，包括递归方式和非递归</h3>

<p>方式</p>

<p>1）递归版本</p>

<p>​	先序 中序 后序的区别在于——在遍历点第几次（每个点都会遍历3次）打印</p>

<div class="language-java highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="mi">1</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">先序</span>
	<span class="kd">public</span> <span class="kd">static</span> <span class="kt">void</span> <span class="nf">preOrderRecur</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="nc">Node</span> <span class="n">head</span><span class="o">)</span> <span class="o">{</span>
